# .rscignore - Control what rsconnect deploys to shinyapps.io
# Only essential files are deployed: app.R, R/ modules, data files, www/ assets

# ============================================================================
# EXCLUDE DOCUMENTATION
# ============================================================================
docs/
*.md
!README.md

# ============================================================================
# EXCLUDE DEPLOYMENT ARTIFACTS
# ============================================================================
rsconnect/

# ============================================================================
# EXCLUDE VERSION CONTROL
# ============================================================================
.git/
.gitignore

# ============================================================================
# EXCLUDE HIDDEN FILES
# ============================================================================
.DS_Store
.Rhistory
.RData

# ============================================================================
# FILES THAT WILL BE DEPLOYED:
#
# ✅ app.R (main application)
# ✅ R/fct_*.R (all function files)
# ✅ R/mod_*.R (all module files)
# ✅ R/utils*.R (utility functions)
# ✅ data_dictionary_enhanced.csv (required data)
# ✅ inst/extdata/instrument_valid_ranges.csv (instrument ranges)
# ✅ www/custom.css (custom styling)
#
# NOTE: All test files and development files have been moved to
#       ../sarcopenia-tests-archive/ directory to prevent deployment issues
# ============================================================================
